 install jenkins using tomcat

 13  java -version

 yum install java-1.8.0-openjdk.x86_64

   15  wget http://mirrors.fibergrid.in/apache/tomcat/tomcat-9/v9.0.12/bin/apache-tomcat-9.0.12.tar.gz
   16  tar -xvzf apache-tomcat-9.0.12.tar.gz -C /opt  
    17 mv /opt/apache-tomcat-9.0.12/ /opt/tomcat
   18  wget http://mirrors.jenkins.io/war-stable/latest/jenkins.war
   19  cp -rv jenkins.war /opt/tomcat/webapps
   20  cd /opt/tomcat/
   21  ll
   22  cd bin
   23  ll
   24  sh startup.sh 
   25  

   to change jenkins security using terminal we just need to do some changes on the config file and for this the given path is - ( vi /var/lib/jenkins/config.xml )

